Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew reached Fishman Island,\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates,\Nwho are plotting to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,alongside Vander Decken, who is after\NMermaid Princess Shirahoshi, move in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves\Ncaught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am the only one who you want to kill, please do not harm the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Wimpyhoshi! I told her to stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like this idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you to save my beloved Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
