Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Noah is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is turning away. It's not gonna crash into the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama saved us by drawing the ship away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--Princess Shirahoshi! --Please escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Shirahoshi? There's no way for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go out to the sea in order to keep the Noah away from the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The bubble can't take any more damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the main entrance is too far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am correct, Luffy-sama's friends were the last ones who left the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe the gateway is still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Isn't there anything that we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our princess is risking her life to save us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not her fault that Decken is after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only is Decken on that ship but now Hody is climbing aboard one of the chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He betrayed me, that lunatic - Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can still be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful for Hody, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishmen are way stronger than humans in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him pierce the bubble and go out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it carefully - not too strong, not too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Armee de L'Air Assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gum Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I in between the bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody! He's still under the bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have stop it! We only have to slow it down a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...before it catches up with Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pull! --Don't let the Noah go any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama! Get somewhere safe while we're slowing it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be out of their minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't move it even a millimeter! How senseless is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Worthless scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of cowards like you guys, humans think they can make fools of Fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives mean nothing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,People like you just keep bringing shame to Fishmen. Drop dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama, escape! H-Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right! The entrance to the palace was left open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stay with me! Damn Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi is going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...out to sea through the gateway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--The Noah is going after her! --Princess-sama, go farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, the chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How inconvenient it must be to be a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You all act so tough on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but you couldn't even win a fight with a Fishman child in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how weak you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you regret standing against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans become powerless in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but for a Fishman like me, this is where I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,can use my true ability to the full extent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very fortunate for me that Shirahoshi went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil Fruit users fare no better than ordinary people in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it ironic, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic and powerless! That's how you truly are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how big you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You humans can't even breathe in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, a piece of trash like you will never become the ruler of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to regret what you did and beg for mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even do that now, can you? You pathetic, lowly creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rot in hell, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That stupid hanger-on - what a useless gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away from me, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have stop it! We only have to slow it down a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...before it catches up with Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pull! --Don't let the Noah go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama! Get somewhere safe while we're slowing it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In order to save the people of the Ryugu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to draw the Noah away from the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...as far as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like your freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer have those walls of Hard Shell Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that were protecting you for last 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a choice of bleeding to death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or being crushed by the giant ship - Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you one last chance, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say "Yes," I'll spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have mercy, Decken-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead and live in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As my beloved wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna let her marry a guy like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our only baby sister! We're not gonna let you hurt her, Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Mamboshi-sama! Brother Ryuboshi-sama! Hoe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not your brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers-sama! Some people at the plaza tried to save me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi! Don't cry now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Brother-sama got mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Father, we can't even let the ship get damaged-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to return it to the seafloor without letting it hit anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! In any case, you shouldn't swim near undersea mountains or trenches!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah will get damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where should I go, Brother Mamboshi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go up! There are too many obstacles down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go beat Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never get away from the Noah and my unending love, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You got hurt before - are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Members of the royal family, soldiers, citizens... all of them got hurt or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And even Shirahoshi is trying so hard to save the Ryugu Kingdom while injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is not the time for me to suffer from such minor injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Merfolk are the greatest swimmers in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me, they look like stop motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dead once it hits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I chop both of you up and feed you to the little fishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirate with a 400 million bounty and the prince of the Ryugu Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What exquisite food for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Although his power is phony, he's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty strong in the sea! Almost like Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to be impressed at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where you go, you can't get away from the Shark Slicer's blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to escape in the cloud of dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shirahoshi! --Hey, go to the deck of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanted to ask me before? But why there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what Jinbe told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the ship is filled with water, Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know but I know Decken is a Devil Fruit user.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there must be air for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier for me to fight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna kick the crap out of Hody and the guy who throws things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Wimpyhoshi when we left the tower, that I was gonna protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of promises...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We three will become great warriors like our father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and protect Shirahoshi with our lives as we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a promise to keep too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We were defeated by that cheap hoodlum who relies on some
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,fake power from the Energy Steroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that we suspected you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. Take me to the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna go to the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of Straw Hat anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something that needs to be done right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Go after him already! --No, wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody has an advantage in the water since he is a Fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,--If nothing is done... --What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go up! Go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's no use, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as my Mark-Mark Curse is in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no way for you to get away from the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Neptune? Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tormenting Shirahoshi with the Noah now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.63,0:22:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen to this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody suddenly attacks Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His terrifying plan was to destroy Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody then attacks Shirahoshi to complete his ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, Luffy's new attack is unleashed on Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Start of an Intense Battle!\NLuffy vs. Hody!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
